*# A = Adjective
*# N = Noun
*# R = Adverb
*# S = Adjective
*# V = Verb

*.22_caliber---------------a| of or relating to the bore of a gun (or its ammunition) that measures twenty-two hundredths of an inch in diameter; "a .22 caliber pistol"  
*.38_caliber---------------a| of or relating to the bore of a gun (or its ammunition) that measures thirty-eight hundredths of an inch in diameter; "a .38 caliber shell"  
*.45_caliber---------------a| of or relating to the bore of a gun (or its ammunition) that measures forty-five hundredths of an inch in diameter
